title: Grateful Dead Live at Cumberland County Civic Center on 1983-10-18
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Dupree's Diamond Blues, CC Rider, Althea, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Might As Well

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider, Estimated Prophet-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Sugar Magnolia, E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text:
Hell yes! So glad a SBD finally surfaced of this fantastic show.  The train sounds etc. in the Rider Jam are so killer.  Way too many highlights to go into.  
Enjoy this one if you are a SBD only head and have missed it up to this point.

1st Set Highlight... .... is Mexicali Blues!
Been looking out for one of these that really stood out from the crowd for ages. Today I found it!
CC Rider is a wild ride too.
